✅ 1. Show Timestamp of Last Save/Load
🔧 Update index.html
Add this below the .stats section:

html

<div class="last-action" id="lastAction"></div>

🧠 In script.js, cache the element:
js

const lastActionEl = document.getElementById('lastAction');

🔁 Add this function:

js

function showTimestamp(message) {
  const now = new Date().toLocaleString();
  lastActionEl.textContent = `${message} at ${now}`;
}

Call this:

After save:

js

showTimestamp("Saved");
After successful load:

js

showTimestamp("Loaded");
